# Re-published bundle note

This bundle was reconstructed by overlaying the code/config corrections from
`hdr_validation_corrected.zip` onto `hdr_validation_extended_bundle.zip` while
preserving the original extended bundle layout, tests, logs, and stage output
artifacts.

Integrated updates:
- corrected source files under `src/hdr_validation/`
- updated `configs/paper_defaults.json`
- added `configs/validation.json`
- added `docs/CORRECTIONS.md`

Additional integration repair applied during re-publication:
- `src/hdr_validation/control/lqr.py` and `src/hdr_validation/control/mpc.py`
  were aligned so `dlqr_robust()` returns `(K_robust, P_robust)` and
  `solve_mode_a()` uses `P_robust` as the terminal Riccati matrix.

The original bundled stage results were preserved; they were not recomputed as
part of this re-publication step.
